0Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人覺得洞爺得呢兩個地方係正 個燈飾唔知今年仲有沒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/190430_372e57774606dc66cdcc1f25a3b77d54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F190430_372e57774606dc66cdcc1f25a3b77d54.jpg&h=615f37d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/190430_4074a95590c0d4360ddfdf299ea2dda3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F190430_4074a95590c0d4360ddfdf299ea2dda3.jpg&h=45faad4e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nthanks巴打<br />\n其實依家個plan有少少變<br />\n<br />\n開頭札幌可能會留多一日<br />\n中間仲諗緊插一插個兩日一夜既洞爺湖<br />\n咁既話青森會直接cancel<br />\n最尾就函館直落東京"},{"pid":"22672e65fc178014153cb4dfbae6f829bbe8584c","tid":398975,"uid":67529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T20:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>感謝上面位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未講完<br />\n<br />\n同巴打一樣都係果幾日去北海道<br />\n不如搵幾日一齊玩？<br />\n特別係滑雪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不了，同囡囡去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我一月頭都係北海道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e135102343ee646a6249e948448cfc7c2c19a41","tid":398975,"uid":146941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:52:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}